This paper is primarily focused on visual complexity analysis, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also mentions the relevance of the dataset to cognitive psychology (cs.HC), visualization and infographics (cs.MM), advertisement (cs.IR), and machine learning (cs.LG). However, since the paper's main contribution is the creation of a visual complexity dataset, cs.CV is the most likely sub-category.
